SIM←{⍺←⍬ ⋄ o n t←⍵ ⋄ e←o↑¨ea ⋄ v i←o↑¨vol mat ⋄ a←o o∘↑¨area
    r e f←n t bc sr wr st(tol min max CPFEH conv)m[i]e a v⊣ts←⎕TS
