    ⍺,⍨10↑¨(2(I¨⍤↑,S¨⍤↓)⍵),(I¨+⌿¯1↑[2]r),⊂D 1e3÷⍨⎕TS-⍥(12⎕DT⊂)ts}
DMN←{H←{i←⍵ ⋄ (⌊dm÷⍨63.8){⊖⍕(⍉⍕⍪(1↓⌊⍵×m[i;⍳⍺])⍴¨'⎕')(⍉⍕⍪(1↓⌊⍵×n[i;⍳⍺])⍴¨'⎕')}÷k}
    k←⍺ ⋄ q m n←⍵ ⋄ ⍕q,⍪H¨⍳≢q}

⎕←'Reading ',file
