⎕←'Running simulation of ',(⍕steps),' steps with ',(⍕grains),' grains'
    ⎕←¯10↑¨7↑¨'grains' 'steps' '∆time' 'iter' 'seconds'
    ⎕←'dc_r.csv' 'dc_tex.csv' 'dc_f.csv'SIM grains steps ∆t
